quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Aagaya Allah ka faisla, ab iske liye jaldi na machao, paak hai woh aur baala-tar hai us shirk se jo yeh log kar rahey hain"
  16,2,"Woh is rooh ko apne jis banday par chahta hai apne hukum se malaika ke zariye nazil farma deta hai (is hidayat ke saath ke logon ko) “aagah kardo, mere siwa koi tumhara mabood nahin hai, lihaza tum mujhi se daro”"
  16,3,"Usne aasman o zameen ko barhaqq paida kiya hai, woh bahut baala o bartar hai us shirk se jo yeh log karte hain"
  16,4,Usne Insaan ko ek zara si boondh se paida kiya aur dekhte dekhte sareehan woh ek jhagdalu hasti ban gaya
  16,5,"Usne jaanwar paida kiye jinmein tumhare liye poshak (clothing) bhi hai aur khurak bhi, aur tarah tarah ke dusre faiyde bhi"
  16,6,Unmein tumhare liye jamal (pleasant look) hai jab ke subah tum unhein charne ke liye bhejte ho aur jabke shaam unhein wapas latey ho
  16,7,Woh tumhare liye bojh dho (utha) kar aisey aisey muqaam tak le jatey hain jahan tum sakht jaanfishani (painful toil) ke bagair nahin pahunch sakte. Haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhara Rubb bada hi shafeeq aur meharbaan hai
  16,8,Usne ghodey (horses) aur khacchar (mule) aur gadhey paida kiya taa-ke tum unpar sawar ho aur woh tumhari zindagi ki raunak baney. Woh aur bhaut si cheezein (tumhare faiyde ke liye) paida karta hai jinka tumhein ilm tak nahin hai
  16,9,Aur Allah hi ke zimme hai seedha raasta batana jabke raaste tedhey bhi maujood hain. Agar woh chahta to tum sabko hidayat de deta